164 bool Dynamixel2Arduino::ping(uint8_t id)
165 {
166  bool ret = false;
167 
168  if (id != DXL_BROADCAST_ID){
169  InfoFromPing_t recv_info;
170  if(Master::ping(id, &recv_info, 1, 10) > 0){
171  if(recv_info.id == id){
172  if(getPortProtocolVersion() == 1.0){
173  recv_info.model_number = getModelNumber(id);
174  }
175  ret = setModelNumber(id, recv_info.model_number);
176  }
177  }
178  }else{
179  uint8_t recv_ids[254];
180  uint8_t recv_cnt;
181 
182  recv_cnt = Master::ping(DXL_BROADCAST_ID, recv_ids, sizeof(recv_ids), 3*253);
183 
184  if(recv_cnt > 0){
185  for (uint8_t i=0; i<recv_cnt; i++){
186  (void)setModelNumber(recv_ids[i], getModelNumber(id));
187  }
188  ret = true;
189  }
190  }
191 
192  return ret;
193 }

197 {
198  bool ret = false;

200  if(id <= 253){

202  ret = (model_number_idx_[id] != 0xFF) ? true:false;
203  if(ret == false){
204  setLastLibErrCode(D2A_LIB_ERROR_UNKNOWN_MODEL_NUMBER);
205  }
206  }else{
207  setLastLibErrCode(DXL_LIB_ERROR_INVAILD_ID);
208  }
209 
210  return ret;

890 int32_t Dynamixel2Arduino::readControlTableItem(uint16_t model_num, uint8_t item_idx, uint8_t id, uint32_t timeout)
891 {
892  int32_t recv_len, ret = 0;
893  ControlTableItemInfo_t item_info;
894 
895  p_dxl_port_ = (SerialPortHandler*)getPort();
896  if(p_dxl_port_ == nullptr){
897  setLastLibErrCode(D2A_LIB_ERROR_NULLPTR_PORT_HANDLER);
898  return 0;
899  }
900 
901  item_info = getControlTableItemInfo(model_num, item_idx);
902 
903  if(item_info.addr_length > 0)
904  {
905  recv_len = read(id, item_info.addr, item_info.addr_length, (uint8_t*)&ret, sizeof(ret), timeout);
906 
907  if(recv_len == 1){
908  int8_t t_data = (int8_t)ret;
909  ret = (int32_t)t_data;
910  }else if(recv_len == 2){
911  int16_t t_data = (int16_t)ret;
912  ret = (int32_t)t_data;
913  }
914  }
915 
916  return ret;
917 }

977 float Dynamixel2Arduino::readForRangeDependencyFunc(uint8_t func_idx, uint8_t id, uint8_t unit)
978 {
979  float ret = 0;
980  int32_t recv_data = 0;
981  uint16_t model_num = getModelNumberFromTable(id);
982  ItemAndRangeInfo_t item_info;
983 
984  // To use the command function without ping() or model addition.
985  if(model_num == UNREGISTERED_MODEL){
986  if(setModelNumber(id, getModelNumber(id)) == true){
987  model_num = getModelNumberFromTable(id);
988  }
989  }
990 
991  if(model_num != UNREGISTERED_MODEL){
992  item_info = getModelDependencyFuncInfo(model_num, func_idx);
993 
994  if(item_info.item_idx != ControlTableItem::LAST_DUMMY_ITEM){
995  recv_data = readControlTableItem(model_num, item_info.item_idx, id);
996  checkAndconvertReadData(recv_data, ret, unit, item_info);
997  }else{
998  setLastLibErrCode(D2A_LIB_ERROR_NOT_SUPPORT_FUNCTION);
999  }
1000  }else{
1001  setLastLibErrCode(D2A_LIB_ERROR_UNKNOWN_MODEL_NUMBER);
1002  }
1003 
1004  return ret;
1005 }

1007 bool Dynamixel2Arduino::writeForRangeDependencyFunc(uint8_t func_idx, uint8_t id, float value, uint8_t unit)
1008 {
1009  bool ret = false;
1010  int32_t data = 0;
1011  uint16_t model_num = getModelNumberFromTable(id);
1012  ItemAndRangeInfo_t item_info;
1013 
1014  // To use the command function without ping() or model addition.
1015  if(model_num == UNREGISTERED_MODEL){
1016  if(setModelNumber(id, getModelNumber(id)) == true){
1017  model_num = getModelNumberFromTable(id);
1018  }
1019  }
1020 
1021  if(model_num != UNREGISTERED_MODEL){
1022  item_info = getModelDependencyFuncInfo(model_num, func_idx);
1023 
1024  if(item_info.item_idx == ControlTableItem::LAST_DUMMY_ITEM)
1025  return false;
1026 
1027  if(checkAndconvertWriteData(value, data, unit, item_info) == false)
1028  return false;
1029 
1030  ret = writeControlTableItem(model_num, item_info.item_idx, id, data);
1031  }else{
1032  setLastLibErrCode(D2A_LIB_ERROR_UNKNOWN_MODEL_NUMBER);
1033  }
1034 
1035  return ret;
1036 }
